function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	idLorath = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "lorath")[1]
	locLorath = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Loc_Lorath")[1]
	idNeyrelle = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "neyrelle")[1]
	locNeyrelle = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Loc_Neyrelle")[1]
	locSphere = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "sphere_loc")[1]
	
	Hydra.ActorInterruptPrimaryPower(idDonan);
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation("QST_Hell_Bombardment_1", idDonan)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idDonan, false)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idDonan, locDonan, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idDonan, locDonan)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idLorath, false)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorath, locLorath, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorath, locLorath)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idNeyrelle, false)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelle, locNeyrelle, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idNeyrelle, locNeyrelle)
	
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idDonan);
	
	Hydra.EventSend("QST_Hell_Battlefield_Ambush_4_MeteorRain");
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	local 	idDonan = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "donan")[1]
			locDonan = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Loc_Donan")[1]
			idLorath = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "lorath")[1]
			locLorath = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Loc_Lorath")[1]
			idNeyrelle = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "neyrelle")[1]
			locNeyrelle = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Loc_Neyrelle")[1]
			idShield = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Shield")[1]
			locSphere = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "sphere_loc")[1]
	
	-- 	Horadrim chanting 
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation("QST_Hell_Horadric_Sphere", idDonan, idLorath)	

	-- 	enable shield invisible actor
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idShield, "QST_Hell_Horadrim_Sphere_Knockback")
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idShield)
	
	-- 	enable horadrim shield vfx
		Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(locSphere, 10)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(locSphere, "fxKit_harmless_persistentBarrierCylindrical_horadric_Impact", true, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, true)
		ID_BUBBLE = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(PROJECTILE_SUPPRESSING_TRIGGER, locSphere, true, 0, 0);
	
	-- 	Donan & Lorath casting
		Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idDonan, "AnimKey_Chant_Ritual_EyeLevel", 0)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idDonan, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric", true)
		Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idLorath, "AnimKey_Chant_Ritual_EyeLevel", 0)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idLorath, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric", true)
	
		Hydra.Wait(1.5);
		
		local tMeteorLocations = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Horde_Meteor_Locations");
	
		if (#tMeteorLocations > 0) then
			ShuffleTable(tMeteorLocations);
			local flTotalMeteorTime = 2.0;
		
			-- 	Meteor rain
			for i, idMeteorAttractor in ipairs (tMeteorLocations) do
				Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idMeteorAttractor, "QST_Hell_Main_Meteor");
				Hydra.Wait(flTotalMeteorTime/#tMeteorLocations)
			end
		end
	
	Hydra.Wait(2.5);
	
	-- 	Disable Horadrim Sphere and enable AI
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idDonan, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idLorath, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(locSphere, "fxKit_harmless_persistentBarrierCylindrical_horadric_Impact")
	Hydra.ActorDelete(ID_BUBBLE);
	ID_BUBBLE = nil;

	Hydra.ActorDisable(idShield)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idDonan)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idLorath)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idDonan, true)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idLorath, true)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idNeyrelle, true);
	
	if (ID_SUCCUBUS ~= nil) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(ID_SUCCUBUS);
		local tLandLocations = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "LAND_LOCATION");
			
		if (#tLandLocations > 0) then
			ShuffleTable(tLandLocations);
				
			Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtTarget(ID_SUCCUBUS, tLandLocations[1], POWER_LAND, true);
		else
			Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtTarget(ID_SUCCUBUS, ID_SUCCUBUS, POWER_LAND, true);
		end
	end
	
	Hydra.EventSend("QST_Hell_Battlefield_Ambush_4_MeteorRain_Over")
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	local idShield = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Shield")[1]
	
	-- Remove VFX from Horadrim and stop phased anim
	for i, tHoradrim in pairs(ID_HORADRIM) do
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(tHoradrim)
		Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(tHoradrim, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric")
	end
	
	-- Disable bubble and VFX on it
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idShield)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idShield, "fxKit_harmless_persistentBarrierCylindrical_horadric")
	
	-- Apply vulnerable debuff after shield bursts
	for i, tDemons in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hell_Horde_Monsters")) do
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget("VulnerableDebuff", "VULNERABLE_DEBUFF", tDemons)
	end
end
